topic.title: Is big tech stepping too far?
topic.body: Is it really their responsibility to control the internet? How is it fair business practice to gang up and take our competition?

topic.title: BTC?
topic.body: Whats everyone's thoughts on BTC? Price targets? Will it continue to grow? Seems like a lot of big money is getting in the crypto space.
